# Hooks Standards

## Rules of Hooks
- Only call hooks at top level (no conditionals, loops)
- Only call from React function components or custom hooks

## Side Effects
- Use useEffect for side effects
- Explicit dependencies array
- Cleanup (return function) for subscriptions, timers, listeners

